name: Anatomy of a Skelton Man
description: I met it after the battle of 1000 (L)eyes. I saw a room in the back of the hall. Opened the door, there it was. The Skeleton Man, Was he the hero Born of Saturn and the Moon? A meteor falling to the earth? A warm fire in the otherwise barren earthen room. With a Single door behind the looming skeletal creature. Skeleton man spoke, a joke of sorts, I lost focus, vision fading, cosmic ejection, eviction... What was behind that door? I must know.
